IMAPAccount migadu
Host imap.migadu.com
User david@daporter.net
PassCmd "pass migadu.com/david@daporter.net"
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore migadu
Account migadu

MaildirStore local
Path ~/Mail/
Inbox ~/Mail/inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel primary
Master :migadu:
Slave :local:
Patterns *
Create Both
#Expunge Both
SyncState *

# For details of the following setting, see
# https://vxlabs.com/2021/03/21/mbsync-copyarrivaldate-yes/
CopyArrivalDate yes